Detailed Description

True dictionary class.

Stores ORVDictValue data types accoring to a string key.

virtual std::string ORDictionary::GetStringOfValue (  )  const [inline, virtual]

Returns a string of the value.

For example, for the number 1, it would return a string "1". This is useful for generating a string output of a dictionary.
